Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.48,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Hyoudou Issei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.79,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a high school sophomore aiming\Nto become the Harem King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:14.45,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,However, I am NOT your\Naverage high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.02,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,That's because I am actually a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:22.00,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,No, really. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.33,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,By a strange turn of events,\NI was reincarnated as a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.71,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I became family to President Rias,\Nwho I greatly admired…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:36.43,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,...and I enjoyed a happy youth\Nwith my many comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:40.11,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,and the legendary\NRed Dragon Emperor inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:44.14,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,One peaceful day, as we were\Nnearing the sports festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:46.62,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,a suitor wanting Asia's hand\Nin marriage appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.42,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,It was the upper-class devil, Diodora Astaroth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:55.53,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how handsome he was\Nand how good his family was,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.12,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I would never accept him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:03.47,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I could never accept anyone who'd step on\NAsia's feelings and forcefully make her his!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:10.88,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Consumed with anger, I was able\Nto defeat Diodora and save Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.63,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:20.35,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Please allow me to pray before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.11,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you going to pray about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:23.77,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.54,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:49.92,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.42,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.92,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,The little sister of the fake Devil King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.64,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Shalba Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:02.76,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I am the true descendant of\Nthe Great Devil Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.39,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Beelzebub?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.72,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Help me, Shalba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.02,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.94,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,If both the old and current devil kings\Ncombine their strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.32,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Shalba, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.41,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.99,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you align yourself with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.20,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Little sister of Sir Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.08,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,This is sudden, but I will have you, relative of\Nthe current devil king, die here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.29,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,The reason you murdered Astaroth\Nand the Glasya-Labolas heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.20,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,You planned this all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.09,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,And you even involved Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.02,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.02,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:47.52,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you go? Come on, we're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.19,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.33,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.87,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We're doing the three-legged\Nrace in the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.45,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We need to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.41,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.21,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,President, Asia isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.37,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We have to find her quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.16,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,She's my... She's our treasured family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.59,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.80,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Truly, the princess of the\NGremory household has bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.01,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,You, red filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.76,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.69,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I sent that girl far beyond the dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.36,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,She has taken her last breath by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.98,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, she is dead.
