Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.63,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Hey, devil. You called yourself Shalba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.63,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,You made the wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.22,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.52,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I, who shall awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.69,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,It started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.19,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:21.11,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,...am the Heavenly Dragon who stole\Nthe principle of domination from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.69,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,It has always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.24,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Right you are. It's always been so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.03,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I laugh at the infinite and fret over the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.62,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,What the world desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.54,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,What the world rejects...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.00,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I shall become the Red Dragon of Domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.54,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,...has always been power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.21,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,...has always been love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:45.17,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I shall drown you in the\Ndepths of crimson purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.97,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,What... is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.76,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,This amount of aura and power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.22,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:58.49,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.73,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Juggernaut Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.38,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.48,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.07,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.46,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.92,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.46,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide! Divide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.13,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Vali's power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.97,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Just how much do you plan to stand in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.35,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.07,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.72,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,President, that isn't Issei anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:15.20,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,You monster! So, this is the Juggernaut Drive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.66,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.46,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,My legs won't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.63,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,The power of Gasper's Sacred Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:39.47,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad. If we stay here, we'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.32,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.32,Ddraig - Top,,0,0,0,,Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.29,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.32,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Rias!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.90,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.82,Ddraig - Top,,0,0,0,,Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.58,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Impossible. I am the descendant\Nof the true devil king...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.58,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,By a mere dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.54,Ddraig,,0,0,0,,Longinus Smasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:12.38,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Red Dragon! White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.40,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Where is Issei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.13,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.46,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.24,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Even though he defeated Shalba,\Nhe isn't reverting back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.88,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're in a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.18,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Vali?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.76,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I only came to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.93,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,To see the Juggernaut Drive\Nof the Red Dragon Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.14,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.94,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't she part of your family?\NThis little healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:20.70,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We happened to come across her while we\Nwere moving through the Dimensional Gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.16,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.08,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia! Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:36.22,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,However, it looks like Hyoudou Issei\Nhad an incomplete transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.43,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.89,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to change him back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.85,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows. If he can't revert himself back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.98,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,he will continue to use his\Nlife force until he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.19,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,--If we tell him that Asia is safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.78,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,--Asia... Asia...\N--If we tell him that Asia is safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.82,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,That's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:59.03,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Just approaching him will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.95,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.17,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I know that it's not our place to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.54,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Please, lend us your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.55,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We will do anything that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.84,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,So please lend us your strength to save Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:25.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,If we could give the depths\Nof his psyche a good shake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.64,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Depths of his psyche...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.81,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,A good shake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.45,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.66,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We just need to show him some boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.58,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Either way, we can't reach him in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.34,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Then, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.83,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song is said to calm the anger\Nof a dragon since ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.88,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,but I've never heard such a tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.17,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:10:59.92,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:00.88,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.34,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.37,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.89,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,It exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.27,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.62,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Shidou... Irina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.42,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is worse than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.09,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Shidou, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.38,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,The bigwigs all have a pretty\Ngood idea of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.22,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Things looked pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:47.95,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,So Devil King Lucifer and Azazel\Nhad me bring in a secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.89,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,And Lord Odin was able to\Ntransport something this big!
