Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.22,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. You don't need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.52,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I’m so happy, I couldn’t help it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.23,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Next in line, please be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.56,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're going to get first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.60,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.90,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia, stay with me forever.\NDon't leave me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.96,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:50.91,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei! Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:51.53,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,--Try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.74,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,--We got first place! All right!\N--Try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:54.61,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,--We got first place! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.83,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it, Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:00.84,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! We did, Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:06.07,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia, please heal him with your Sacred Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:08.83,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,You won't be seen behind the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.18,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:13.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei, please lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.31,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.10,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Asia, try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:38.19,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Asia. I feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.40,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to participate in\Nthe rest of the events now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:46.95,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei, I wasn't able to say this because\Nyou were sleeping the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.82,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,A-Asia?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.15,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:16.16,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I will always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:20.75,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,Issei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:32.48,Tensai_Main,,0,0,0,,I will love you forever, Issei.
